      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Classic JRPG style games are all but immortal now and the genre is in a very comfortable spot where we all know that no matter how much time passes, there will never be a drought of new games to try out. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Sword of Elpisia",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is one of the earliest ones in 2022, putting the player in a world where technology is based around magitools and magical instruments that are used for varied purposes (such as keeping monsters away or manipulating water). The twist comes when the game delves deeper into the Magiswords, bladed weapons that are created from living beings. With the territory of classic style JRPGs, there’s a certain level of expectation when it comes to worldbuilding, story, characters and gameplay - can ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Sword of Elpisia",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " and the developers at KEMCO deliver on said expectations?",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=19RtULbwRys",
        "html": "<iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/19RtULbwRys?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>",
        "metadata": {
          "title": "RPG Sword of Elpisia - Official Trailer",
          "author_name": "KEMCO",
          "author_url": "https://www.youtube.com/user/KemcoGames",
          "height": 113,
          "width": 200,
          "version": "1.0",
          "provider_name": "YouTube",
          "provider_url": "https://www.youtube.com/",
          "thumbnail_height": 360,
          "thumbnail_width": 480,
          "thumbnail_url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/19RtULbwRys/hqdefault.jpg"
        },
